Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Daisy Jo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You here to pick up some cookies\Nto go with your milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh ya, Pinkie, don'tcha know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mrs. Cake just baked a fresh batch\Nof your favorite oatmeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds delightful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose, your calla lilies look even better\Nthan last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you'll take first prize\Nat the flower show again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Pinkie.\NWould you like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking fit as a fiddle, Mr. Waddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're wearing my favorite tie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw shucks Miss Pinkie,\Nyou flatterer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, happy birthday, Cheerilee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy day-after-your-birthday, Zecora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lovely hi, Miss Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And Miss Matilda, happy birthday to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...in one hundred and thirty two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, how do you remember\Neverything about everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:03:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause everypony's my friend\Nand I love to see my friends smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My name is Pinkie Pie\N(Hello!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I am here to say\N(How ya doin?){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna make you smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I will brighten up your day!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't matter now\N(What's up?){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you are sad or blue\N(Howdy!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'Cuz cheering up my friends{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is just what Pinkie's here to do!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'Cuz I love to make you smile, smile, smile!\N(Yes I do!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It fills my heart with sunshine all the while!\N(Yes it does!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'Cuz all I really need's a\Nsmile, smile, smile!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From these happy friends of mine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I like to see you grin!\N(Awesome!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love to see you beam!\N(Rock on!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The corners of your mouth turned up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is always Pinkie's dream!\N(Hoof bump!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if you're kind of worried{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And your face is made of frown{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll work your heart and do my best{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To turn that sad frown upside down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'Cuz I love to make you grin, grin, grin!\N(Yes I do!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Busted out from ear to ear, let it begin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just give me a joyful\Ngrin, grin, grin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you fill me with good cheer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's true, some days are dark and lonely{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And maybe you feel sad{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Pinkie will be there to show you\Nthat it isn't that bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is one thing that makes me happy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And makes my whole life worthwhile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:05:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's when I talk to my friends\Nand get them to smile!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really am so happy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your smile fills me with glee!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I give a smile, I get a smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's so special to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'Cuz I love to see you beam, beam, beam!\N(Yes I do!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me what more can I say to make you see\N(That I do!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It makes me happy when you\Nbeam, beam, beam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, it always makes my day!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on everypony, smile, smile smile!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fill my heart up with sunshine, sunshine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I really need's a\Nsmile, smile, smile!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From these happy friends of mine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on everypony, smile, smile, smile!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fill my heart up with sunshine, sunshine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I really need's a\Nsmile, smile, smile!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From these happy friends of mine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the perfect gift for me!\N(Come on everypony, smile, smile, smile!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a smile as wide as a mile!\N(Fill my heart up with sunshine, sunshine!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To make me happy as can be!\N(All I really need's a smile, smile, smile!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To make me happy as can be!\N(From these happy friends of...){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Smile! Smile! Smile! Smile! Smiiiiiile!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on and smile!\N(Smile!){\i0}
