Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, you're smarter than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! I'm Pinkie Pie.\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Property of C.D.D."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing that last "D"\Nis for Donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick as a whip, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how about that C...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin? Calhoun? Caleb? Carl? Carmine?\NCarlo? Charlie? Chester? Chico?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Claudio? Cleetus? Clifford? Coraline?\NCornelius? Cortez? Crank? Christopher?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cranky! It's Cranky, alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:06:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And your middle name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Doodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry?\N- Doodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Doodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a Cranky Doodle Donkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're a Cranky Doodle Donkey guy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Cranky Doodle Donkey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never met you,\Nbut you're my new friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm your best friend Pinkie Pie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon now, Doodle. Give a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony calls me Doodle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meet somepony new, check.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Introduce myself, check.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sing random song outta nowhere, check.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become instant best friends... uncheck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it, how can somepony\Nnot become instant best friends with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it something I said?\NWas it something I sang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time for the blame game,\NPinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's somepony new in town,\Nand you need to win him over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"Try everything you can to make\NCranky smile and be your friend".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna win Cranky's friendship,\Nyou're gonna have to bring your A game!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy doody, Cranky Doodle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So... are you moving to Ponyville,\NCranky?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What gave you the hint there, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The cart full of stuff, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd be happy to show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the least a new friend can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, kid, I traveled around Equestria\Nmy entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made many friends.\NI don't need any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh! I could never have\Ntoo many friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you go\Nand make some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't need to go,\Nwhen I can stay and make friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Cranky, you can call me Pinkie.\NAll of my friends do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to Ponyville for some peace\Nand quiet and privacy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to be alone with my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is to get to my new home\Nand unpack my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this bauble do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at these!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie! Keep your hooves off my wagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Cranky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised not to touch your wagon\Nso I brought one of my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I use it to welcome folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'da guessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can be wagon buddies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've gotta at least let me\Ngive you the special welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome welcome welcome{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A fine welcome to you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome welcome welcome\NI say how do you do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome welcome welcome\NI say hip hip hurray{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome welcome welcome\Nto Ponyville today!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, silly me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I must've put the confetti in the oven\Nand the cake in the confetti cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Still delicious!\NTry some, Cranky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sure to make you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Spider! Big hairy spider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that your wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can fix this, I can fix this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everypony!\NDoes anypony have a toupee?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This donkey is really, really, bald!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?\NThis is serious business, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Cranky needs a new wig\Nto cover his hairless head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're losing him, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Cranky, please!\NLet me make it up to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please please please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies, this is a spa emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Cranky needs help, STAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Cranky, I have a gift for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The spa treatment was gift enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to\Nexplode or anything, promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a new toupee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I had my friend Rarity make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She calls it the "dreamboat special".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wonderful.\NThanks, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's starting to warm up,\Nbut still no smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Whatcha doing there,\Nol' buddy ol' pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a yard sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you two bits for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not selling, kid.\NI'm unpacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so pretty!\NWhere'd you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Manehattan, now put it down, gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What were you doin' there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to find a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always trying to find friends,\Nand today I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,See how good I am at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a special friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Like me?\N- No, you're extra special, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in Equestria did you get this,\NCranky?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fillydelphia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awfully pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it was. I mean, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's pretty, now put it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Cranky got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you look at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Cranky!\NCan I ask you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you sa-yayayayay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There!\NAll better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not all better, all soggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Cranky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're sorry, well, then,\Neverything is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- It is?\N- No! It isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, kid,\NI will never be your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Never, or never-ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Never, ever, ever, ever, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's four "ever"s.\NThat's like... forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cranky said he would never forever\Nbe my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this is hard for you, Pinkie.\NSeeing that you're friends with everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But you just have to accept that Cranky\Nis gonna be an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He just... doesn't want to be bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he doesn't want to be bothered\Nby your over-the-top super-hyper antics.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's okay, Twilight.\NI get what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're both saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess... I can leave Cranky alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after he accepts my apology!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Cranky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!\NLeave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that you don't want me\Nas a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just wanted to say "I'm sorry"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you accept my apology?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Cranky! Please accept my apology!\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm really, really, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really, really,really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Really. Really. Really. Really.\NReally. Really. Really. Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Cranky, please, please accept my apology!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd do anything to make it up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You ruined my book!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You destroyed all I have\Nto remember her by!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Her?\NHer who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The special friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away, Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Cranky? It's me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that you don't wanna\Nbe my friend or accept my apology...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I leave you alone forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to at least try\Nto make up for ruining your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want it, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you would give me is sure\Nto lead to some sort of disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, you really are cranky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be... is it really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It can, and it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Matilda! But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I never told you about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I put two and two and two together\Nand it added up to Matilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well when you were talking about\Nyour souvenirs,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you said something about trying to find\Na special friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And y'know, I wasn't just born yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My birthday isn't for\Nanother seventy five days!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, in your scrapbook,\Nthere was a flower, an old ticket,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and a menu from the Grand Galloping Gala!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knew I recognized all these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But how could you have\Never seen them before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I also have them in my scrapbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd seen them in Matilda's book!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Matilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The night we met at the gala\Nwas the most magical night of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't wait to see you again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when I came to your room\Nthe next day, you were gone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't you get my note?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I never got it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since that day,\NI've gone from town...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to town... to town...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching all over Equestria for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Until finally I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to Ponyville\Nto retire from my search.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was living in Ponyville\Nthe whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I always hoped that some day\Nyou would come and find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Doodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Matilda?\NNopony calls him Doodle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony... but Matilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Doodle, I'm so happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So does this mean\Nthat you accept my apology?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Pinkie, I accept your apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And, I am honored to call you my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can hang out together,\Nand chat, and sing songs, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,party!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can throw you guys a big party!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be called "Welcome to Ponyville,\NI found my lost love...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm BFF's with Pinkie Pie" Party!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe something less over-the-top\Nand not so super-hyper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, we're eternally\Ngrateful to you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Matilda and I just want to spend some\Ntime together in peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're still friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, you went way, way, way\Nout of your way to make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Princess Celestia,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there are many different kinds of friends,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and many ways to express friendship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Some friends like to run and laugh\Nand play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But others just like to be left alone,\Nand that's fine too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the best thing about friendship\Nis being able to make your friends smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had a Cranky Doodle sweetheart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's his Cranky Doodle joy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I helped a Cranky Doodle boy, yeah{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I helped a Cranky Doodle boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, privacy, sorry.
